Console commands for Android project

------------------------------------------------------------------------
create release icon:
$convert -size 512x512 -define gradient:center=192,256 -define gradient:radii=384,384 radial-gradient:white-#3eb12f background.png
$convert cover.png -resize 460x460 -gravity center -background none -extent 512x512 image.png
$convert background.png image.png -compose over -composite icon.png
	
------------------------------------------------------------------------
create release feature image:
$convert -size 1024x500 -define gradient:center=192,256 -define gradient:radii=700,384 radial-gradient:white-#3eb12f feature-bg.png
$convert feature-bg.png image.png -compose over -composite feature.png

------------------------------------------------------------------------
build android project:
executed from project directory
$gradlew build

------------------------------------------------------------------------
list attached devices
$adb devices -l
List of devices attached
6Z7BH0EO36             device product:rk3188 model:Evolio_X10 device:rk3188 transport_id:1


------------------------------------------------------------------------
publish android project on github:
executed from project directory

$git init
after execution local git repository is created on hidden directory .git

commit project content to local repository
last dot is for current working directory 
$git add .
$git commit -m "Initial import"

create empty! project on github
add remote origin
$git remote add origin https://github.com/kids-cademy/atlas.vegetables.git

push local repository to remote origin, master branch
$git push --set-upstream origin master
